&lt;h2&gt;National Selection for Oral &amp; Maxillofacial Surgery&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Specialty Training Level 1 (ST1)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Commencing from August 2021&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for approximately 10 vacancies in the Oral &amp; Maxillofacial Surgery Training Programme at Level One (ST1) across Deaneries/HEE local offices in England, Scotland and Wales starting from August 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful candidates will progress from ST1 through to ST7 without further interview, subject to satisfactory annual reviewand award of CCT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The interviews will be online via MS Teams on the 8th of February 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The application window opens on the 5th of November 2020 and closes on the1st of December 2020 at 4.00 pm(UK time).You will not be able to submit your application after this time. Please ensure that you have completed all the relevant sections of the application forms missing information will deem your application incomplete and it will not be considered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must apply via the online recruitment system Oriel. Oriel can be accessed from the link provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The qualifications and professional registration requirements plus other eligibility criteria can be found in the person specification. The person specification for this specialty is available with in Oriel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please visit the Oral &amp; maxillofacial surgery recruitment website, which can be accessed through Oriel,to find the following information:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The full application process including further details of the multi-specialty recruitment assessment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Details of the posts available including the expected rotation details&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anticipated outcome of the training programme, subject to satisfactory progression&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Travel and relocation expenses policy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
